### ReleaseCenter V2 API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询发布中心列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/release-center/releases?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询发布详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/release-center/releases/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 回滚发布版本（写接口需幂等与防伪）
# 回滚后应可在 RuntimeExecutions-V2 / Runtime audit-trails 中追溯到 release.rollback 与 runtime.route.rebind 审计
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/release-center/releases/1/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{login.response.headers.X-CSRF-TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
